-- Australia to Update Economic Forecast, Confirm Surplus Tomorrow, ABC Says
-- Malcolm Scott
-- 2010-07-13T09:15:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/australia-to-update-economic-forecast-confirm-surplus-tomorrow-abc-says.html

          
          
             Australian Treasurer Wayne Swan will
release an updated economic forecast tomorrow that will include
details on projected revenue from a revised mining tax and may
confirm the budget will return to surplus in 2013, Australian
Broadcasting Corp. news reported on its website, without saying
where it got the information.  
